{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id0cf5819c-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1071"},"text":"§ 1071.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Statement of purpose; nondiscrimination; and appropriations authorized","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0cf5819d-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Purpose; discrimination prohibited","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf5819e-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Purpose","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The purpose of this part is to enable the Secretary—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf5819f-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/a/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to encourage States and nonprofit private institutions and organizations to establish adequate loan insurance programs for students in eligible institutions (as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1085"},"text":"section 1085 of this title","children":[],"tail":"),"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581a0-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/a/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to provide a Federal program of student loan insurance for students or lenders who do not have reasonable access to a State or private nonprofit program of student loan insurance covered by an agreement under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1078/b"},"text":"section 1078(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":","}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581a1-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/a/1/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to pay a portion of the interest on loans to qualified students which are insured under this part, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581a2-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/a/1/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to guarantee a portion of each loan insured under a program of a State or of a nonprofit private institution or organization which meets the requirements of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1078/a/1/B"},"text":"section 1078(a)(1)(B) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581a3-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Discrimination by creditors prohibited","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"No agency, organization, institution, bank, credit union, corporation, or other lender who regularly extends, renews, or continues credit or provides insurance under this part shall exclude from receipt or deny the benefits of, or discriminate against any borrower or applicant in obtaining, such credit or insurance on the basis of race, national origin, religion, sex, marital status, age, or handicapped status.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581a4-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization of appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For the purpose of carrying out this part—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581a5-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" there are authorized to be appropriated to the student loan insurance fund (established by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1081"},"text":"section 1081 of this title","children":[],"tail":") (A) the sum of $1,000,000, and (B) such further sums, if any, as may become necessary for the adequacy of the student loan insurance fund,"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581a6-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" there are authorized to be appropriated, for payments under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1078"},"text":"section 1078 of this title","children":[],"tail":" with respect to interest on student loans and for payments under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1087"},"text":"section 1087 of this title","children":[],"tail":", such sums for the fiscal year ending "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1966-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1966","children":[],"tail":", and succeeding fiscal years, as may be required therefor,"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581a7-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" there is authorized to be appropriated the sum of $17,500,000 for making advances pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1072"},"text":"section 1072 of this title","children":[],"tail":" for the reserve funds of State and nonprofit private student loan insurance programs,"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581a8-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" there are authorized to be appropriated (A) the sum of $12,500,000 for making advances after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1968","children":[],"tail":", pursuant to sections 1072(a) and (b) of this title, and (B) such sums as may be necessary for making advances pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1072/c"},"text":"section 1072(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":", for the reserve funds of State and nonprofit private student loan insurance programs,"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581a9-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/b/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" there are authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary for the purpose of paying a loan processing and issuance fee in accordance with ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1078/f"},"text":"section 1078(f) of this title","children":[],"tail":" to guaranty agencies, and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581aa-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/b/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" there is authorized to be appropriated, and there are appropriated, out of any money in the Treasury not otherwise appropriated, such sums as may be necessary for the purpose of carrying out ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1072/c/7"},"text":"section 1072(c)(7) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"Sums appropriated under paragraphs (1), (2), (4), and (5) of this subsection shall remain available until expended, except that no sums may be expended after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 2010","children":[],"tail":", with respect to loans under this part for which the first disbursement is after such date. No additional sums are authorized to be appropriated under paragraph (3) or (4) of this subsection by reason of the reenactment of such paragraphs by the Higher Education Amendments of 1986."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581ab-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Designation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The program established under this part shall be referred to as the “Robert T. Stafford Federal Student Loan Program”. Loans made pursuant to sections 1077 and 1078 of this title shall be known as “Federal Stafford Loans”.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581ac-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Termination of authority to make or insure new loans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding paragraphs (1) through (6) of subsection (b) or any other provision of law—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581ad-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" no new loans (including consolidation loans) may be made or insured under this part after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 2010","children":[],"tail":"; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581ae-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1071/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" no funds are authorized to be appropriated, or may be expended, under this chapter or any other Act to make or insure loans under this part (including consolidation loans) for which the first disbursement is after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 2010","children":[],"tail":","}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"except as expressly authorized by an Act of Congress enacted after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-03-30"},"text":"March 30, 2010","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id0cf581af-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/329/tIV/s421"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–329, title IV, § 421","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/498/tIV/s402/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–498, title IV, § 402(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/1353"},"text":"100 Stat. 1353","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/297/tII/s2601/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–297, title II, § 2601(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-04-28"},"text":"Apr. 28, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/330"},"text":"102 Stat. 330","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/369/s8"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–369, § 8","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-07-18"},"text":"July 18, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/837"},"text":"102 Stat. 837","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/325/tIV/s411/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–325, title IV, § 411(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", (c), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-07-23"},"text":"July 23, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/510"},"text":"106 Stat. 510","children":[],"tail":", 511; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/244/tIV/s411"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–244, title IV, § 411","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-07"},"text":"Oct. 7, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/1673"},"text":"112 Stat. 1673","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/171/tVIII/s8004/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–171, title VIII, § 8004(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-02-08"},"text":"Feb. 8, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/158"},"text":"120 Stat. 158","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/227/s6/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–227, § 6(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-05-07"},"text":"May 7, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/746"},"text":"122 Stat. 746","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/152/tII/s2201"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–152, title II, § 2201","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-03-30"},"text":"Mar. 30, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/1074"},"text":"124 Stat. 1074","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id0cf581b0-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id0cf581b1-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id0cf581b2-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Higher Education Amendments of 1986, referred to in subsec. (b), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/498"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–498","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/1268"},"text":"100 Stat. 1268","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1001"},"text":"section 1001 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id0cf581b3-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Another ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/244/s411"},"text":"section 411 of Pub. L. 105–244","children":[],"tail":" enacted subpart 8 (§ 1070f et seq.) of part A of this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"id0cf581b4-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 1071, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/329/tIV/s421"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–329, title IV, § 421","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1965-11-08"},"text":"Nov. 8, 1965","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/79/1236"},"text":"79 Stat. 1236","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/460"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–460","children":[],"tail":", §§ 2(b)(3), 3(a), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-08-03"},"text":"Aug. 3, 1968","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/635"},"text":"82 Stat. 635","children":[],"tail":", 636; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/575/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–575, title I","children":[],"tail":", §§ 113(b)(1), 114(a), 119(b), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-10-16"},"text":"Oct. 16, 1968","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/1021"},"text":"82 Stat. 1021","children":[],"tail":", 1027; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/482/tI/s127/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–482, title I, § 127(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-12"},"text":"Oct. 12, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/2099"},"text":"90 Stat. 2099","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/43/s1/a/8"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–43, § 1(a)(8)","children":[],"tail":"–(10), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1977-06-15"},"text":"June 15, 1977","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/91/213"},"text":"91 Stat. 213","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/374/tXIII/s1391/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–374, title XIII, § 1391(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", (2), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-03"},"text":"Oct. 3, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/1503"},"text":"94 Stat. 1503","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/79/s6"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–79, § 6","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-08-15"},"text":"Aug. 15, 1983","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/97/482"},"text":"97 Stat. 482","children":[],"tail":", related to statement of purpose of, appropriations for, and implementation of programs to provide low-interest insured loans to students in institutions of higher education, prior to the general revision of this part by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/498"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–498","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id0cf581b5-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2010—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/152/s2201/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–152, § 2201(1)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “, except that no sums may be expended after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 2010","children":[],"tail":", with respect to loans under this part for which the first disbursement is after such date” after “expended” in concluding provisions."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/152/s2201/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–152, § 2201(2)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (d)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2008—Subsec. (b)(6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/227"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–227","children":[],"tail":" added par. (6)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2006—Subsec. (b)(5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/171"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–171","children":[],"tail":" substituted “a loan processing and issuance fee” for “an administrative cost allowance”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1998—Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/244"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–244","children":[],"tail":" struck out heading and text of subsec. (d). Text read as follows: “Notwithstanding any other provision of this part, no new loan guarantees shall be issued after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1994","children":[],"tail":", if the Secretary does not issue final regulations implementing the changes made to this part under the Higher Education Amendments of 1992 prior to that date. The authority to issue new loan guarantees shall resume upon the Secretary’s issuance of such regulations. This subsection shall not provide the basis for avoiding any requirements for notice and public hearing on such regulations.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1992—Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/325/s411/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–325, § 411(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (c) and struck out former subsec. (c) which read as follows: “The program established under this part shall be referred to as the ‘Robert T. Stafford Student Loan Program’. Loans made under this part shall be known as ‘Stafford Loans’.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/325/s411/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–325, § 411(c)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (d)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"tex